sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (ext-proc)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sidecar as P/D Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prefiller as vLLM Prefiller<br/>(remote)
    participant Decoder as vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP
    participant vLLMZMQ as vLLM KV-Events<br/>5556/TCP ZMQ

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Standard Inference (Non-Disaggregated)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP
    GW->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC (request headers)
    EPP->>K8s: Watch InferencePool, Pods<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    Note over EPP: Plugin pipeline:<br/>Filters → Scorers → Select endpoint
    EPP-->>GW: Routing decision<br/>(selected pod endpoint)
    GW->>Decoder: Forward request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    Decoder-->>GW: Inference response
    GW-->>Client: JSON response

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP
    GW->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC (request headers)
    Note over EPP: Profile handler decides:<br/>disagg vs non-disagg<br/>(prefix-based or always-disagg)
    EPP-->>GW: Routing decision with headers<br/>x-prefiller-host-port, target pod
    GW->>Sidecar: Forward to decode pod<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Note over Sidecar: NIXL v2 connector activated
    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (prefill request)
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>(KV transfer params in body)
    Note over Sidecar: Extract KV params:<br/>block IDs, cache tokens
    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS (decode + KV params)
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming response<br/>(token generation)
    Sidecar-->>GW: Stream response back
    GW-->>Client: Streaming JSON response

    Note over Client,vLLMZMQ: Flow 3: KV Cache State Updates

    loop Real-time KV Events
        vLLMZMQ->>EPP: ZMQ PUB/SUB<br/>5556/TCP (cache events)
        Note over EPP: KV-Block Indexer processes events<br/>Updates Prefix Store
        Note over EPP: precise-prefix-cache-scorer<br/>uses updated state for routing
    end

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 4: EPD Mode (Multimodal, Encoder-Prefiller-Decoder)

    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP (multimodal content)
    GW->>EPP: ext-proc callback<br/>gRPC
    Note over EPP: Multimodal decider detects<br/>image/video content
    EPP-->>GW: Routing with headers<br/>x-encoder-hosts-ports, x-prefiller-host-port

    rect rgb(255, 249, 196)
        Note over Sidecar: EPD Protocol
        GW->>Sidecar: Forward to decode pod<br/>HTTPS
        Note over Sidecar: Fan-out: encode multimodal items
        Sidecar->>Prefiller: Encode + Prefill stage<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        Prefiller-->>Sidecar: KV transfer params
        Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode with KV context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
        Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming tokens
        Sidecar-->>Client: Streaming response
    end
